In re Mark KEY, Attorney. No. 208P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 27, 2007. David R. Johnson, for State Bar. Derrick C. Mertz, Assistant Attorney General, for State of NC.

Prior report: ___ N.C.App. ___, 643 S.E.2d 452.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 27th day of April 2007 by Respondent for Temporary Stay:

"Motion for Stay Dissolved by order of the Court in conference this the 27th day of June 2007."
